Soothing Rain
Discworld ritual help
Soothing Rain

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Soothing Rain - Summons a healing rain shower.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a healing ritual used by Pishites.  When performed, it will
summon a small rain storm into the room, blessed with holy healing
power, which will cure wounds and diseases of anyone who comes into
contact with it.  You will need the holy symbol of your god to
perform this ritual.
.EP
